\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Standardization of Bias and Fairness Auditing:
\f0\b0  While the need to audit AI for bias is widely recognized, there is currently a lack of standardized, validated, and widely accepted methodologies for conducting these audits in a healthcare context. An cross-disciplinary effort is required to develop robust standards and best practices for fairness evaluation, ensuring that these critical assessments are performed consistently and rigorously across different systems and institutions.
